         <div type="translation">
            <ab>The holy church to Petros, oeconomos (of the churcg of) Kosmas. Give the widow Sophia from the coats which you have for good use one coat, total 1 coat only. (2nd hand) Greetings. (1st hand) Year 156 = 125, Mecheir 1 of the 3rd indiction.</ab>
